description:
We got a chance to talk to Chris Potter after a set at the Chicago Jazz Showcase.  
Check out his new album The Dreamer Is The Dream on iTunes 
http://smarturl.it/DreamerDream_iTu
title: Artist Spotlight #9: Chris Potter
